-----------------------------------------------------------------
iMage is an web image viewer written in Opa (http://opalang.org).

Author: Adam Koprowski <Adam.Koprowski@mlstate.com>
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Compilation & usage
-------------------
- put some images you want to browse in the './imgs' directory
- compile & run with: 'make run'
- go to 'localhost:8080' and have fun :)

